    <p class="section-number">07 · Why operators call us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Seven reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>EPA 608 Universal certified.</strong> Required for any sealed system work. Many residential shops claim "we do commercial too" without 608. That's illegal. See our <a href="/credentials/epa-certified/">EPA 608 page</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>24/7 phone answering, no emergency surcharge.</strong> $120 diagnostic is $120 whether Tuesday morning or Saturday midnight.</li>
